VOCSZ
Frequency list per GDM

targets.queryText:
WITH gdm_percentiles AS (
    SELECT gdm_id, word_rank, PERCENT_RANK() OVER(ORDER BY word_rank) PercentileRank
    FROM VOCSZ_frequency_list
    INNER JOIN test_cases
    ON VOCSZ_frequency_list.test_id = test_cases.test_id
    WHERE gdm_id = (${gdm1Name:singlequote})
    ORDER BY word_rank ASC
)

SELECT word_rank AS 'Word rank > 0.95 percentile'
FROM gdm_percentiles
WHERE PercentileRank > 0.95
LIMIT 1;

targets.queryText:
SELECT test_cases.test_id, word_rank, count(frequency), word, PERCENT_RANK() OVER(ORDER BY word_rank) PercentileRank
